IRS990.Desc: Operation and maintenance of a home for dependent aged members known as Moosehaven. Moosehaven assumes full responsibility for total care of residents, including providing food, clothing, housing, and medical and dental care. It also benefits the community by aiding in extending the lives of residents and enabling them to live safe, useful and independent lives and to relieve stress.

SupplementalInformationDetail.ExplanationTxt: Endowment funds will help facilitate the perpetual operation of Moosehaven.
The cost of travel for spouses of the Directors of Moose International are included in the individual's form W-2 or Form 1099 NEC.

SupplementalInformationDetail.FormAndLineReferenceDesc: Form 990, Part VI, Section A, Line 6
SupplementalInformationDetail.ExplanationTxt: Moose International is the sole member of Moosehaven, Inc. and they elect the Directors of Moosehaven, Inc.

SupplementalInformationDetail.FormAndLineReferenceDesc: Form 990, Part VI, Section A, Line 7a
SupplementalInformationDetail.ExplanationTxt: Moose International, as sole member, appoints the members of the Moosehaven governing body.

SupplementalInformationDetail.FormAndLineReferenceDesc: Form 990, Part VI, Section A, Line 7b
SupplementalInformationDetail.ExplanationTxt: Moose International, as sole member, must approve or ratify actions outside the normal course of business.

SupplementalInformationDetail.FormAndLineReferenceDesc: Form 990, Part VI, Section B, Line 11b
SupplementalInformationDetail.ExplanationTxt: A draft of the form is sent to all Directors and Officers for review and comment. Once they have responded, all comments are addressed and the final version is released.

SupplementalInformationDetail.FormAndLineReferenceDesc: Form 990, Part VI, Section B, Line 12c
SupplementalInformationDetail.ExplanationTxt: Annually, Directors, Officers and Key Employees sign a statement affirming they are not a party to any transaction which might give rise to a conflict of interest.

SupplementalInformationDetail.FormAndLineReferenceDesc: Form 990, Part VI, Section C, Line 19
